3 (c) The board may not consider claims for reimbursement submitted less than 1,000 days following
4 the facility's last state-required compliance inspection.
5 (4) The board shall review and approve each request that meets the requirements of this section,
6 inform the owner or operator of the approval, and reimburse the owner or operator from the fund.
